    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dummy Dungeon, despite its colorful visuals, offers fast-paced gameplay from a first-person view that requires the player's mechanical skills and concentration, and in addition, gives the player a great deal of freedom to create his unique playstyle as the player makes it through the dungeons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Various locations</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore different corners of the world; from dark dungeons to huge flying machines, all filled with unique enemies and tons of items to collect.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/ed891600d2ec981b33d1fef6ff53811e.avif?t=1765555395\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique characters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 24 playable characters. Use a grappling hook as a Monk or produce powerful enhancements in a cauldron as a Witch. The effects offered by a character drastically affect dungeon combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/ff026e951e300385ec3a714f169d78f8.webp?t=1765555395\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/ff026e951e300385ec3a714f169d78f8.poster.avif?t=1765555395\" class=\"bb_img\" width=480 height=480 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerful perks and upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modify your stats and weapons as you go, customize your equipment according to your own vision to save the beautiful princess. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each perk can be upgraded with additional copies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/87a3a2227560ffcdaf5604fda82dbd41.avif?t=1765555395\" width=500 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Large arsenal of unique weapons</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A huge number of weapons with unique enhancements. Weapon effects vary greatly from a simple critical hit or fire enhancement to effects that completely change the effect of the weapon such as knockup, creating zones, flying behind the player, gaining gold, etc.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/3deac0132a7ce34c9e598a2225efed7f.poster.avif?t=1765555395\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/3deac0132a7ce34c9e598a2225efed7f.webm?t=1765555395\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1891030/extras/3deac0132a7ce34c9e598a2225efed7f.mp4?t=1765555395\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenging fights and interesting bosses</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each floor ends with a battle against a powerful opponent with multiple attacks and abilities, making the fights very dynamic.</p>",
